text: Match.com is an online dating website. It serves 25 countries in more than eight languages. The company headquarters is in Dallas, Texas. It also has offices in West Hollywood, San Francisco, Tokyo, Rio de Janeiro, and Beijing. Match.com is owned by IAC."IAC's Match.com Announces Successful Tender Offer For Meetic S.A." 18 August 2011 Reuters.
